### MCP (Model Context Protocol) API Tests
### Tests for McpController endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080
### OpenCode server: http://localhost:4096

### Get all MCP servers
### Returns a list of all configured MCP servers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get MCP server status
### Returns the status of a specific MCP server
# @prompt name Replace with actual MCP server name
GET http://localhost:8080/api/mcp/{{name}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Start MCP authentication
### Initiates the OAuth authentication flow for an MCP server
# @prompt name Replace with actual MCP server name
POST http://localhost:8080/api/mcp/{{name}}/auth/start
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Handle MCP OAuth callback
### Handles the OAuth callback from an MCP server
# @prompt name Replace with actual MCP server name
POST http://localhost:8080/api/mcp/{{name}}/auth/callback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "oauth_authorization_code",
  "state": "oauth_state_parameter"
}

###

### Remove MCP authentication
### Removes stored authentication for an MCP server
# @prompt name Replace with actual MCP server name
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/mcp/{{name}}/auth
Content-Type: application/json

###
